<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/85212770-elliott-b">Elliott B.</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I highly recommend We Are The Ants over A Boy Worth Knowing. I would say they are very lightly connected. I agree with Abby Bartle in saying A Boy Wor<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I highly recommend We Are The Ants over A Boy Worth Knowing. I would say they are very lightly connected. I agree with Abby Bartle in saying A Boy Worth knowing is more similar to Wonders of the Invisible World--I can absolutely see that connection on many levels.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
