              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2215878198606029965">I&apos;m happy I found this book.<br/>This is one of the best YA book thIs year. <br/>I almost had the feeling like when I read Aristotle and Dante.<br/>All the teenage problems along with ghosts intact...is one unique experience. <br/>In my real life, I am the aunt Susan with my seeing and talking with ghost niece. Trust me it&apos;s not easy. And it&apos;s real.<br/><br/>Nice sweet story, low angst and with typical teenage problems to solve. This book is unputdownable and worth every time you took to read. And reread.<br/>Because, you don&apos;t r</span>
  <span id="freeText2215878198606029965" style="display:none">I'm happy I found this book.<br />This is one of the best YA book thIs year. <br />I almost had the feeling like when I read Aristotle and Dante.<br />All the teenage problems along with ghosts intact...is one unique experience. <br />In my real life, I am the aunt Susan with my seeing and talking with ghost niece. Trust me it's not easy. And it's real.<br /><br />Nice sweet story, low angst and with typical teenage problems to solve. This book is unputdownable and worth every time you took to read. And reread.<br />Because, you don't read a good book only once :)<br /><br />Highly recommended!</span>
  <a data-text-id="2215878198606029965" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

